  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "ClearAll[x, p, pp, q1, q2, hbar, eta, t1, t2, m, w]\r\n\r\n(* Kernel T(x,p-p') *)\r\nT[x_, p_, pp_] :=\r\n  DiracDelta[p - q2 - pp] +\r\n   2 Cos[q2 x/hbar] DiracDelta[p - q2/2 - pp] +\r\n   DiracDelta[p - pp];\r\n\r\n(* w_{ε,k}(x,p') *)\r\nwk1t1[x_, pp_] :=\r\n  (w[x - pp t1/m, pp - q1] +\r\n    2 * Cos[(q1/hbar) (x - pp t1/m)] * w[x - pp t1/m, pp - q1/2] +\r\n    w[x - pp t1/m, pp]);\r\n\r\n(* Convolution *)\r\nwk1t1k2 =\r\n  Integrate[\r\n    T[x, p, pp] * wk1t1[x, pp],\r\n    {pp, -Infinity, Infinity},\r\n    Assumptions -> {\r\n      Element[{p, q1, q2, x t1, m, hbar}, Reals],\r\n      m > 0, hbar > 0\r\n    }\r\n  ] // FullSimplify\r\n\r\n\r\nwk1t1k2 // Expand // Collect[#, _w, FullSimplify] &",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wexpr\"><wgraph class=\"resizable\" style=\"width:1043px;height:110px;\" aspect-ratio=\"0.1051\" tabIndex=\"-1\"><img class=\"invert-brightness\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" /></wgraph></div>",
