  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "Propagate[expr_, t_] :=\r\n   expr /. x -> x - p t/m;\r\n\r\nwk1t1k2t2 = Propagate[wk1t1k2, t2] // FullSimplify\r\nwk1t1k2t2 // FullSimplify // Apart // Collect[#, _w, Simplify] &\r\nwk1t1k2t2 //. {\r\n (2 m x - 2 p (t1+t2) + q2 t1)/(2 m) :>\r\n    x - p (t1+t2)/m + q2 t1/(2 m),\r\n\r\n (m x - p (t1+t2) + q2 t1)/m :>\r\n    x - p (t1+t2)/m + q2 t1/m\r\n}\r\n\r\nTeXForm[wk1t1k2t2]\r\nInputForm[wk1t1k2t2]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
