  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "ClearAll[x, p, \\[Sigma]x, \\[Sigma]p];\r\n\r\n$Assumptions =\r\n  Element[{x, p, \\[Sigma]x, \\[Sigma]p}, Reals] &&\r\n  \\[Sigma]x > 0 && \\[Sigma]p > 0;\r\n  \r\nw[x_, p_] :=\r\n  Exp[-x^2/(2 \\[Sigma]x^2) - p^2/(2 \\[Sigma]p^2)]\r\n",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
